{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"**1. Fixed step-level agent config leaking between steps** (`internal/agent/runner.go`)","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386737549Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- The `stepExecutor.Execute` method was directly mutating the shared `prompt.Adapter.Commands` and `ExplicitArgs` fields. Step-level `agent_command`/`agent_args` overrides would persist to subsequent steps, causing them to use the wrong agent.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386742208Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- Fixed by saving and restoring the original values via `defer`.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386757507Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386766894Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"**2. Added default args for well-known agents** (`internal/adapters/agents/prompt/prompt.go`)","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386771383Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- Added `gemini` with `[\"-p\"]` default args","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386779729Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- Added `codex` with `[\"--full-auto\"]` default args","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386783446Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- Exported the map as `DefaultAgentArgs` for testability","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386787273Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386794437Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"**3. Added fallback logging** (`internal/adapters/agents/prompt/prompt.go`)","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386798434Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- When an agent in the fallback chain fails and the system tries the next one, it now logs: `[fallback] step \"X\": agent \"Y\" failed (...), trying \"Z\"`","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386805738Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- When a fallback agent succeeds, it logs: `[fallback] step \"X\": using agent \"Y\" (primary agents failed)`","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386809735Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- Uses `StatusWriter` when available, falls back to standard logger","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:38:17.386816989Z"}
